            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1393220/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            启蒙运动与现代性的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2913181">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2913181/" class="title-link">资本主义意识形态的罩门</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2913181"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/faramita/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1269807-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/faramita/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">人生天地间，忽如远行客</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-05 02:05:31</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2913181_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  某种意义上说，启蒙与现代是祛魅后的西方世界的新宗教。所谓的普世价值都由此演生。 对启蒙与现代性的反思戳中了资本主义意识形态的罩门。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2913181/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2913181_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2913181_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
